dave hale's home page welcome to dave hale's home at sep dave 1991 if you have a java enabled browser try out the latest reincarnation of the fast fourier transform lab the source code is freely available you may download a copy of the paper atomic meshes from seismic images to reservoir simulation published in september 2002 in the proceedings of the 8th european conference on the mathematics of oil recovery an earlier related paper atomic images a method for meshing digital images was published in october 2001 in the proceedings of the 10th international meshing roundtable
